body:
backport of #26703

This PR includes all latest nanoAOD developments, as recently merged in the master branch, with the exclusion of things that were not ported (e.g. L1 unprefireable bit).

Also here we need cms-data/PhysicsTools-NanoAOD#5, as it was done in cms-sw/cmsdist#4937, should some additional step be taken to add it to 10_2_X integration environment?
title: NanoAOD developments: 190508 version [102X]
